  "text": "In this subsection we discuss a simplified implementation of ABIP. In particular, we show that the dual variables p and q in (9), (10) and (11) can be eliminated using a proper initialization. The framework of our analysis is similar to the one in [CITATION_1] , but the techniques we use are quite different because the Moreau decomposition cannot be directly applied to (u, v) when the log-barrier penalty function is used. The main technical result is summarized in the following theorem.",
